   </td></tr></table>
   </blockquote>
   
<p>
   <table><tr><td width=2 bgcolor="#cc0000"></td>
   <td>
   <b><font color="#cc0000">
   Exercise RCORR.7:</font></b> 
   
   Show that Var(r<sub>R</sub>) = 1/(n-1) under H<sub>0</sub>
   
   </td></tr></table>
   </blockquote>
   
<p>

<table><tr><td bgcolor="#cccccc">
<b>Theorem:</b>

Under H<sub>0</sub>, 

<blockquote>
sqrt(n-1) r<sub>R</sub> ~ AN(0,1).
</blockquote>


</td></tr></table>

